Square shower enclosures usually consist of 2 lines of glass that intersect at a 90-degree angle.  They are usually at a corner of the bathroom bounded by 2 firm walls.
Neo shower enclosures consist of 3 lines of glasses with the angle of intersection being greater than 90 degrees- typically 135 degrees.

Curtain Wall Systemystem
Curtain Wall Construction
- 
A curtain wall system is an outer covering of a building in which the outer walls are non-structural, utilized only to keep the weather out and the occupants in.
since the curtain walling is non-structural, it can be made of lightweight materials, thereby reducing construction costs.
- 
Functions of curtain wall in buildings
•Elimination of water penetration, facade system.
•Air impermeability
•Resistance to wind, thermal and acoustic actions
- 
Types of curtain wall system
•Stick curtain wall system
•Unitized curtain wall systems
- 
Components of curtain wall, structural elements
1. Transoms
2. Mullions
3. Vision glass
4. Anchor

fields.title: Why Choose Omokaa
fields.body:
Millions of people now prefer to find solutions online. It is quick, easy and convenient. Omokaa provides you with a platform that connects you with these people who may be a solution to your problem or need. At Omokaa, there are so many choices and you can get through the options that you have quickly. You can get exactly what you are looking for, no applications, no crowded malls, no parking, no screaming kids. Your solution is just a few clicks away.

The proliferation of the internet gives entrepreneurs from every walk of life and from every geographic location access to a global audience of buying consumers, eager sellers, information, and resources as in no other time in history. The internet has not only made it easier to sell products into the global marketplace utilizing online sales venues such as omokaa but to also source a nearly limitless number of in-demand products, which can be bought cheaply from domestic and overseas suppliers and resold for a handsome profit. 
At omokaa the mantra of every buy-and-sell enterprise is simple, and easily memorized. With the simple click of a mouse you can buy products cheaply from thousands of suppliers spanning the globe, and resell these same products on the same platform at the comfort of your palms or fingers. Our easy to use features enable you to easily post items for sale and keep tabs of offers and bids from potential buyers privately and securely. As a buyer, you can also invite offers from sellers by posting the products you ae looking to purchase. We guarantee that you will come to the end of your search in no time. 
For the employer, omokaa saves you the time of having to peruse hundreds of applications physically to find your potential employee. We provide you with an interface to sieve through applications efficiently and tirelessly so that you only get to view the applications that are closest to your ideal candidate for the role. 
As a job seeker, all you have to do is upload your curriculum vitae and/or portfolio and wait for that important call from your next employer. Professionals can also post their works for exhibition or even interact in our numerous groups hosting different topical issues relevant to their hustles. 
Omokaa is your ideal partner as far as buying or selling, recruitment or job seeking is concerned. We connect you to millions of people in one platform but you get to choose who to interact and/or trade with. As a matter of fact, omokaa is your to go to e-commerce partner.

What is e-commerce

E-commerce, also known as electronic commerce or internet commerce, refers to the buying and selling of goods or services using the internet, and the transfer of money and data to execute these transactions. E-commerce is often used to refer to the sale of physical products online, but it can also describe any kind of commercial transaction that is facilitated through the internet. Whereas e-business refers to all aspects of operating an online business, e-commerce refers specifically to the transaction of goods and services.
In today’s competitive and convenience focused society, no longer do consumers want to venture to the high street in order to buy or sell items, instead consumers want to shop or sell from their own homes, making e-commerce a flexible solution for both businesses and buyers.
E-commerce is an ideal way you can take your hustle from a traditional brick and mortar store to an innovative, well-loved brand. By offering great products 24 hours a day along with online customer service, blogs and social media, no longer is your business one singular store, with an online presence your business can be the home of your products and the general home of your business, allowing you to fully expand your product ranges without having to worry about moving locations or worrying about not being able to expand your hustle.

What is a hustle

Hustling means that you work hard. It means that you toil every single day. It means doing things other people will not do, and you do them with a sense of joy and purpose because you love it.  It means working smarter. In this sense, Omokaa values your hustle and gives you a platform that will catapult you to higher levels. 
Hustling is really about moving and shaking, about seeking opportunity around every corner, and in every conversation, wherever you can find it in a business sense. Hustlers do not make money in one or two ways, they make money in various Ways. Many of those ways complement each other like diverse irons in the fire.
Hustlers see the big picture, but they don’t necessarily a traditional plan, they are often street savvy and good communicators who will squeeze a dollar out of a dime. They pride themselves in making something out of nothing. They use their raw talents to convert their ideas, life experience and whatever expertise they have into cash. At Omokaa we host your hustle online without you having to worry about e-commerce fraud. 

E-commerce fraud  
e-commerce fraud is said to be the wrongful or criminal deception intended to result in financial or personal gain. Research has shown that fraud in e-commerce has substantially increased globally over the last few years with the immense rise in online marketplaces. With more sophisticated technology available to fraudsters, it has only become more difficult for e-commerce businesses to keep a track of the tactics used to defraud online businesses.
With cybercriminals becoming more and more sophisticated, merchants and retailers at Omokaa can depend on us to detect and prevent cyberthreats so that they can go about their hustles without having to look over their shoulder with worry. We have a secure sophisticated system which ensure that all data and information uploaded or shared is safe. We host a secure chat friendly system and update our systems periodically and introduce features to be able to respond to complex emerging security issues for our subscribers’ ultimate protection.
Omokaa has developed and still develops many services and protocols to secure your privacy and data whenever you subscribe or visit us. We harness internal as well as external mechanisms to ensure that every aspect of your security is completely covered. On this backdrop, there is no doubt that omokaa is a fast-rate, if not the best e-commerce website for your hustling needs.
best e-commerce website
Omokaa offers one of the best marketing tools to a business or need. As you strive to grow it is very likely you will want a partner to grow with and enlarge your target audience, as well as develop your business for customer requirements and consumer demand. Omokaa lets you scale your business accordingly, allowing you to add more lines, add more payment options and even grow when you choose to ship to, without having to worry about changing your location or moving to a larger premise like you might with a brick and mortar store.

Due to the internet’s accessibility, millions of people across the world can view your post at any time, meaning that for those looking to expand their target and reach out to a larger audience, you have many more opportunities to do so. Compare the amount of people you can reach through a website to the amount you can reach through a high street store or local advertising. There is every reason you should consider omokaa if you are looking to improve your reach. 

Omokaa values your hustle and as such, offers you a whole range of opportunities, from marketing opportunities to increasing your audience ranges to generating more sales and with an optimised and well-developed product we can not only assist you achieve these goals but also offer your customers round the clock, convenient service, that can boost your business or solve your needs.

fields.title: How to post on Omokaa
fields.body:
Posting ads on omokaa.com is easy and fast, just take the following steps to
proceed:

1. Sign up at omokaa.com/login
2. Go to homepage omokaa.com and select the relevant field, whether you want to buy, sell, hire or work.
3. Fill in the required information on the next tab by filtering your choices in
accordance to your preferred category and sub-category.
4. Describe the hustle you want to share.
5. Choose an optional maximum of ten photos to accompany your description.
6. Enter your location.
7. Finally, submit your post.
8. If you choose to create your post first before signing up/in, you will be redirected to the registration/login page
page upon finishing and want to submit.
9. Be ready to receive numerous interested potential clients to promote your hustle.
Good luck with your hustle!
